Question & Options:
In the movie 'Fifty Shades Freed' released in 2017, how did the soundtrack perform on the Billboard 200 chart?
Options:
A. It debuted at #1 with 100,000 equivalent album units.
B. It debuted at #3 with 75,000 equivalent album units.
C. It debuted at #5 with 58,000 equivalent album units.
D. It did not chart on the Billboard 200.
Correct Answer: It debuted at #5 with 58,000 equivalent album units.
